#. <section class="sutta" id="sn35.159"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.159:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.159:0.2"
msgid "16. Nandikkhayavagga"
msgstr "16. The End of Relishing"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 159. Bāhiraaniccanandikkhayasutta → bahiddhānandikkhayayonisosuttaṃ (bj) | nandikkhaya 4 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.159:0.3"
msgid "159. Bāhiraaniccanandikkhayasutta"
msgstr "159. Focus, the Exterior, and the End of Relishing"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.159:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Rūpe, bhikkhave, yoniso manasi karotha, rūpāniccatañca yathābhūtaṃ "
"samanupassatha."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, properly attend to sights. Truly see the impermanence of sights."

msgctxt "sn35.159:1.2"
msgid ""
"Rūpe, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yoniso manasikaronto, rūpāniccatañca yathābhūtaṃ "
"samanupassanto rūpesupi nibbindati."
msgstr "When a mendicant does this, they become disillusioned with sights."

msgctxt "sn35.159:1.3"
msgid "Nandikkhayā rāgakkhayo;"
msgstr "When relishing ends, greed ends. When greed ends, relishing ends."

msgctxt "sn35.159:1.4"
msgid "rāgakkhayā nandikkhayo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.159:1.5"
msgid "Nandirāgakkhayā cittaṃ suvimuttanti vuccati."
msgstr "When relishing and greed end, the mind is said to be well freed."

msgctxt "sn35.159:1.6"
msgid "Sadde …"
msgstr "Properly attend to sounds …"

msgctxt "sn35.159:1.7"
msgid "gandhe …"
msgstr "smells …"

msgctxt "sn35.159:1.8"
msgid "rase …"
msgstr "tastes …"

msgctxt "sn35.159:1.9"
msgid "phoṭṭhabbe …"
msgstr "touches …"

msgctxt "sn35.159:1.10"
msgid ""
"dhamme, bhikkhave, yoniso manasi karotha, dhammāniccatañca yathābhūtaṃ "
"samanupassatha."
msgstr "thoughts. Truly see the impermanence of thoughts."

msgctxt "sn35.159:1.11"
msgid ""
"Dhamme, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yoniso manasikaronto, dhammāniccatañca "
"yathābhūtaṃ samanupassanto dhammesupi nibbindati."
msgstr "When a mendicant does this, they become disillusioned with thoughts."

msgctxt "sn35.159:1.12"
msgid "Nandikkhayā rāgakkhayo;"
msgstr "When relishing ends, greed ends."

msgctxt "sn35.159:1.13"
msgid "rāgakkhayā nandikkhayo."
msgstr "When greed ends, relishing ends."

msgctxt "sn35.159:1.14"
msgid "Nandirāgakkhayā cittaṃ suvimuttanti vuccatī”ti."
msgstr "When relishing and greed end, the mind is said to be well freed.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.159:1.15"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
